summary: Here is my altmer character that i created because i could not find any that interested me and so i decided to take a stab at this myself, hope you guys like her! :)
descriptionHtml:
This is my very first mod so if something is missing in the description or something please tell me :)

Screenshots are more than welcome if you guys want to post yours!



HOW TO INSTALL: just unzip and copy the file to your Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/ChargGen/Presets Folder

HOW TO UNINSTALL: Delete my file from the same folder that you installed it in = Done


Mods required to make her look like in the pictures:

[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] By Expired
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url] By [b]Kalilies, Stealthic, Khaos and Shocky
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?]Ethereal Elven Overhaul[/url] By Nuska[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url] By LogRaam
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url] By Hello Santa
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] By HHaleyy
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62639/?]Empyrean Warpaints[/url] By Empyrean42

If anyone wants to know the Body used in the pictures is:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]Caliente's Beatiful Bodies Edition -CBBE-[/url] By Ousnius and Caliente

With this slider setup:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/66801/?]CBBE-Evolution Body[/url] By Lillysdad2009



All credit goes to the talented and hard working modders mentioned above, i just fiddled with the sliders  ;)


If i failed to give credit to someone or failed to list some required mods please let me know so i can correct this. 


PERMISSIONS: Please do not reupload this mod anywhere else and if you want to make her in to a follower you CAN without asking for my permission separately just give me credit for the preset and we good ^^ Oh and this will be a free mod from here to eternity :)
author: Rolacoasta
